OL,3,CPolitician reprimanded for 'unhelpful
OL,4,Cand unfair' social media posts
OL,6,FA Guernsey politician has been removed
OL,7,Ffrom a police oversight board after
OL,8,Fwhat has been described as a string of
OL,9,F'unhelpful and unfair' social media
OL,10,Fposts.
OL,12,FDeputy Rob Curgenven has been a long-
OL,13,Ftime critic of the island's justice
OL,14,Fsystem, but Home Affairs believes his
OL,15,Fmost recent observations could put
OL,16,Findividuals at risk.
OL,18,FIt comes as the politician posted a
OL,19,Fvideo online about a closed
OL,20,Finvestigation into historical sexual
OL,21,Foffences.
