OL,6,FThe Committee for Home Affairs
OL,7,Fbelieves Deputy Curgenven broke the
OL,8,Fterms of his engagement on the Police
OL,9,FComplaints Committee (PCC) sub-
OL,10,Fcommittee, prompting them to axe him
OL,11,Ffrom the board.
OL,13,FThe reprimanded deputy has told ITV
OL,14,FNews that he is "disappointed" and
OL,15,F"sad" in how the situation has been
OL,16,Fhandled.
