OL,3,CPolitician reprimanded for 'unhelpful
OL,4,Cand unfair' social media posts
OL,6,F"I think the idea of the group is very
OL,7,Fworthy and very appropriate," he
OL,8,Fexplained. "Under the circumstances,
OL,9,Fwhere trust is lacking, I'm just
OL,10,Freally sad because I felt that I had a
OL,11,Flot to give.
OL,13,F"I know the legislation back to front,
OL,14,Fso to take me off the group, I think
OL,15,Fit's a waste."
