OL,3,CPolitician reprimanded for 'unhelpful
OL,4,Cand unfair' social media posts
OL,6,FIt seems his most recent observations
OL,7,Fand the public discussions which
OL,8,Ffollowed on social media - which led
OL,9,Fto the naming of certain individuals
OL,10,Fwho were involved by third parties -
OL,11,Fcrossed the line in the eyes of Home
OL,12,FAffairs.
OL,14,FDeputy Marc Leadbeater, President of
OL,15,Fthe Committee for Home Affairs,
OL,16,Fallegedly told Deputy Curgenven on
OL,17,Fsocial media that it was his
OL,18,F"commenting on a live criminal matter"
OL,19,Fthat had resulted in the decision.
