OL,6,FHowever, Deputy Curgenven also says he
OL,7,Freceived an email saying the reason
OL,8,Ffor his removal was for
OL,9,F"inappropriate" comments.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Committee for Home
OL,12,FAffairs stated: "We agreed we would
OL,13,Fall refrain from commenting in the
OL,14,Fpublic domain on live or individual
OL,15,Fcases and maintain the same rules the
OL,16,FCommittee follows around
OL,17,Fconfidentiality.
