OL,6,F"Deputy Curgenven later agreed to
OL,7,Ffollow the same terms as the rest of
OL,8,Fus, but has since broken them by
OL,9,Fcommenting about individual police
OL,10,Fmatters, including live criminal
OL,11,Finvestigations."
OL,13,FDeputy Curgenven asserts he 'doesn't
OL,14,Fknow where he stands' on where he went
OL,15,Fwrong.
