OL,3,CPolitician reprimanded for 'unhelpful
OL,4,Cand unfair' social media posts
OL,6,F"I have asked publicly for evidence of
OL,7,Fwhere I have breached the terms of
OL,8,Fengagement, and where I have commented
OL,9,Fon a live matter or complaint, but so
OL,10,Ffar, no one has given me any
OL,11,Finformation."
OL,13,FDeputy Curgenven still sits on the
OL,14,FCommittee for Education, Sport, and
OL,15,FCulture, where he says he is "trying
OL,16,Fto get more openness and transparency"
OL,17,Ffrom the States of Guernsey.
