OL,6,FITV News asked if Deputy Curgenven
OL,7,Fwould appeal the decision to be
OL,8,Fremoved, but he believes there is no
OL,9,Fappeal.
OL,11,F"I would (go back) because all
OL,12,Fdeputies are here for the people and
OL,13,Ffor the people's interests.
OL,15,F"I perceive I have something of value
OL,16,Fthat will help the process, so
OL,17,Fgrievances aside, as professionals,
OL,18,Fyou put those disagreements aside, and
OL,19,Fyou work for the betterment of the
OL,20,Fcommunity."
